Classes in sagma.core.model used by sagma.core.data.generator.planetoid
Constructable
           
ModelConstructor
          Allows the user to build one model piece by piece in a very neat manner The next step should be to set a texture, shader or both using 'setTexture(Texture)' and 'setShader(Shader)' Not setting these will leave it as a default WHITE fill Then use 'addTriangle(Triangle)' or 'addQuad(Quad)' to make triangles and quads.
